		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You whisper, your words overlapping and amplifying in a horrendous way in your target's mind, overwhelming their thoughts and compelling them to get away from you.</em></p><p><strong>[[/save wis]]{Wisdom Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage]] damage* and must immediately use its reaction, if available, to move as far away from you as it can using the safest route. They provoke attacks of opportunity, but can attempt to avoid attacks of opportunity if multiple routes are available.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage, no other effect.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Upcasting:</strong> Target one additional creature for each spell level above 1st.</p>",
